'''Novial'''

An interlanguage. 

Novial = Nov International Auxiliari Lingue 
(New International Auxiliary Language).

An interlanguage developed by the Danish linguist Professor Otto Jespersen.

An interlanguage based on Romance languages, English, German, Latin and Scandinavian languages and published in 1928.

